[tb_start_text mode=3]
Any world is full of contradictions.[l][r]
[r]The lament of countless creatures who were unjustly exterminated.[l][r]
Innocent people hanged just to satisfy the vanity of the powerful.[l][r]
Towns and villages burned for no reason.[l][r]
On that very day, someone who seemed happy takes their own life.[l][r]
[r]Before my memories of the "other world" came back, all of this seemed strange to me. The stories of this real world did not flow correctly like in books, but were cruel tales.[l][r]
It's an imperfect world. Yet, the cold reality is that this is the truth.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm]
[bg time="1000" method="crossfade" storage="news.jpg"]
[tb_start_text mode=3]
On the train ads, at the edge of the newspapers, on talk shows, and news on the internet, tragedies shine like stars, sensationally told.[l][r]
People are captivated by them. They watch from the outside as if these stories have nothing to do with them, but that's mistaken, it's real.[l][r]
A world that continues to turn with contradictions.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[bg time="1500" method="crossfade" storage="lastroot.jpg"]
[tb_start_text mode=3]
[r]Now, I don't feel that contradiction anymore.[l][r]
The memories of living in a world just for the two of us, painful but fun. That world ruthlessly taught me everything.[l][r]
[r]The world has always been full of contradictions and despair from the start.[l][r]

[_tb_end_text]

[cm]
[bg time="1500" method="crossfade" storage="lastwall2.jpg"]
[tb_start_text mode=3]
Is that why?[r]
I no longer know what I truly want.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm]
[bg time="1000" method="crossfade" storage="white.png"]
[bg time="1000" method="crossfade" storage="black.png"]
[bg time="1500" method="crossfade" storage="sinen.png"]
[tb_start_text mode=3]
Chi-chan said,[l][r]
This world is too fulfilled, and that's why it can't be satisfied... she said.[l][r]
[r]You really mean that...?[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm]
[bg time="1500" method="crossfade" storage="bigwall.jpg"]
[tb_start_text mode=3]
In the ruins of a city where no matter how hard we searched, we found nothing, in the pure white blizzard, in the pitch-black darkness, Chi-chan led me forward, looking straight ahead, looking up.[l][r]
After losing hope in the world, having fun as much as I could, thinking it didn't matter what happened next, even though my heart was shaking, Chi-chan showed me that living was the best.[l][r]
[r]It was really... Chi-chan who taught me that.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[bg time="1000" method="crossfade" storage="lastwall.jpg"]
[tb_start_text mode=3]
[r]...Do you not realize? Have you already forgotten?[l][r]

Now, Chi-chan seems to be always looking down[r]
Desperately searching for something she knows isn't there, crouched down, unable to walk.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm]
[bg time="1500" method="crossfade" storage="tenji3.jpg"]
[tb_start_text mode=3]
...I remember how hard it was watching Chi-chan struggle to fix the broken vehicle.[l][r]
...But Chi-chan was really amazing back then.[l][r]
Even though it was sad, very sad, even when crying and screaming loudly, after taking a bath, drinking a beer, and taking a rest... she started walking again.[l][r]

[r]...I understand now, Chi-chan.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm]
[bg time="1500" method="crossfade" storage="yoru1.jpg"]
[tb_start_text mode=3]
It's not like that now. We don't need to aim high or walk long distances carrying heavy burdens.[l][r]
There's a convenience store right outside the apartment. A little operation on the smartphone and anything can be delivered.[l][r]
[r]...That's not inherently good or bad, right? If that's the kind of world it is, then that's fine.[l][r]
[r]That's what I think, but for now, I can't say anything.[l][r]
I don't want to deny what Chi-chan says... I never want to tell her she's wrong.[l][r]
I want to grant her every wish.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm]
[tb_start_text mode=3]
Because if I don't watch over Chi-chan, she'll be left all alone again...[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm]
[bg time="1000" method="crossfade" storage="white.png"]
[bg time="1000" method="crossfade" storage="black.png"]
